  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2744650/extras/c2f4102dd00b211e5415305c03dc30be.poster.avif?t=1725387679\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2744650/extras/c2f4102dd00b211e5415305c03dc30be.webm?t=1725387679\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2744650/extras/c2f4102dd00b211e5415305c03dc30be.mp4?t=1725387679\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>A large crater on the moon houses a secret research facility for an experimental cure for cancer. For some time, its transmitting signal stopped responding, and the intervention group sent there was annihilated after a few hours of the mission.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2744650/extras/5377da105d2b4925856af2e570eeba5c.poster.avif?t=1725387679\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2744650/extras/5377da105d2b4925856af2e570eeba5c.webm?t=1725387679\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2744650/extras/5377da105d2b4925856af2e570eeba5c.mp4?t=1725387679\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Take control of a genetically modified commando codenamed XV-11 and try to recover priceless samples from deep inside the laboratory. The process won't be easy, as the lunar base hides many dark secrets...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2744650/extras/796df7b32f92bb01fdc6555c8b45b037.poster.avif?t=1725387679\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2744650/extras/796df7b32f92bb01fdc6555c8b45b037.webm?t=1725387679\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2744650/extras/796df7b32f92bb01fdc6555c8b45b037.mp4?t=1725387679\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>\"The Moon 2044\" is a top down shooter game set in the dark atmosphere of a secret facility located on the moon. Using several different weapons that you will find during the campaign, you must get to the very center of the facility and complete all the objectives set by HQ of NCIS. Immerse yourself in a series of missions in the campaign, in which you will explore a huge military laboratory and face dozens of enemies at once.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2744650/extras/2262806f9a554cb16eb1e7c3656ecf00.poster.avif?t=1725387679\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2744650/extras/2262806f9a554cb16eb1e7c3656ecf00.webm?t=1725387679\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2744650/extras/2262806f9a554cb16eb1e7c3656ecf00.mp4?t=1725387679\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2744650/extras/c2f4102dd00b211e5415305c03dc30be.poster.avif?t=1725387679\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2744650/extras/c2f4102dd00b211e5415305c03dc30be.webm?t=1725387679\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2744650/extras/c2f4102dd00b211e5415305c03dc30be.mp4?t=1725387679\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>A large crater on the moon houses a secret research facility for an experimental cure for cancer. For some time, its transmitting signal stopped responding, and the intervention group sent there was annihilated after a few hours of the mission.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2744650/extras/5377da105d2b4925856af2e570eeba5c.poster.avif?t=1725387679\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2744650/extras/5377da105d2b4925856af2e570eeba5c.webm?t=1725387679\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2744650/extras/5377da105d2b4925856af2e570eeba5c.mp4?t=1725387679\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Take control of a genetically modified commando codenamed XV-11 and try to recover priceless samples from deep inside the laboratory. The process won't be easy, as the lunar base hides many dark secrets...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2744650/extras/796df7b32f92bb01fdc6555c8b45b037.poster.avif?t=1725387679\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2744650/extras/796df7b32f92bb01fdc6555c8b45b037.webm?t=1725387679\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2744650/extras/796df7b32f92bb01fdc6555c8b45b037.mp4?t=1725387679\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>\"The Moon 2044\" is a top down shooter game set in the dark atmosphere of a secret facility located on the moon. Using several different weapons that you will find during the campaign, you must get to the very center of the facility and complete all the objectives set by HQ of NCIS. Immerse yourself in a series of missions in the campaign, in which you will explore a huge military laboratory and face dozens of enemies at once.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2744650/extras/2262806f9a554cb16eb1e7c3656ecf00.poster.avif?t=1725387679\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2744650/extras/2262806f9a554cb16eb1e7c3656ecf00.webm?t=1725387679\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2744650/extras/2262806f9a554cb16eb1e7c3656ecf00.mp4?t=1725387679\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
